reviewText: Amazing video. Well done interviews and outstanding music. Songwriters, Poets, and Folk-singers create their works to comfort the disturbed people and to disturb the comfortable people. When their time here is finished, they leave us their treasures and we bring them back to join us each and every time we read, share, and play their work. Nathan Davis will always live. Much Love and Peace be with you all
This is an amazing account of the life and times of one of the greatest, most missed singer songwriters of the state of NC.
